---
title: Indian Lentil, Chicken & Veggie Coconut Dhal with Herby Flatbreads
description: Dhal is the ultimate bowl of goodness – rich in protein, a good source of fibre and full of aromatic flavours. The coconut milk
balances the spices to create a meal that's both delectable and nourishing.

